item.description:
A big dog meet up... please large breeds only. We would love to play with labs, shepards, mixes and other friendly pooches that won't feel intimidated by a scardy-cat rottweiler who just wants to understand what these other dogs are doing! because of her uncertainty, isabelle acts like a tough guy so she can make the first move, instead of worry about the other dog scaring her first.

we would love to meet for a walk around the big field and take our time to be social and get to know each other over a period of time. isabelle does not make friends instantly, but once she does, look out! she would romp right all over any human that gets in the way.
item.how_to_find_us: Near the pavillion in the middle of the park
